eddy.lang.parser

Class Compiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • eddy.lang.parser.Compiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompilerConstants

    public class Compiler
extends java.lang.Object
implements CompilerConstants
    Translates Policy objects into Compilation objects. It is assumed that all policy objects have a NAMESPACE attribute defined, otherwise the default namespace (see CompilerConstants.NS will be used. The compiler employs the RoleValueVisitor pattern to compile the Role in an Action object.
    Author:
    Travis Breaux
